•DIACAP POA&M; 
•R12 Requirements Management & Traceability Plan (GOLD Requirements Traceability Matrix (RTM) with cross reference to BEA, SFIS, Federal Financial Management Improvement Act of 1996 (FFMIA) controls, Federal Information Security Management Act of 2002 (FISMA) controls; 
•Compliance Management Plan and process updates; 
•Change Management process, plan, & materials updates; 
•PMO Communications Plan & materials updates; 
